Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.78,0:01:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了  香波快用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.48,0:01:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下班的时候我去买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.98,0:01:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买跟现在一样的没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.11,0:02:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人用得很快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.81,0:02:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗头水啦沐浴液什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 今晚吃什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.75,0:02:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想吃的东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.76,0:02:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那等我去了超市再想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.85,0:02:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.69,0:02:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实想菜谱真的蛮有趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为想到有人在家等着吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之  几点回来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.59,0:02:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平常一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.74,0:02:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.62,0:02:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果晚回来的话给我电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平常一样吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.51,0:02:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.79,0:02:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.24,0:02:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就觉得不妥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长的样子有些奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.40,0:03:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像老是盯着我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.86,0:03:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算迟钝如你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也该发觉些什么吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然得盯着你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天晓得你们会做出什么傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再说一遍？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.74,0:03:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  注意舉止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  就这事呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.06,0:03:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.67,0:03:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  给我站住  屎壳郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.77,0:03:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.95,0:03:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是上司监督部下的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.55,0:03:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看那眼神都觉得怪异
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多半是垂涎我们的美色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.57,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滋生了什么危险的邪念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.12,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该不会被卖到什么地方去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西被卖掉了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真由 我们去打扫大堂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.48,0:03:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.97,0:04:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车辆起步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.21,0:04:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一站  榉综合医院前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要下车的乘客请按铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.66,0:04:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.85,0:04:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.87,0:04:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天都来真是辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.10,0:05:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你看上去好像很疲劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特地赶来见女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.37,0:05:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不能给她看到\N这副有如阴霾的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要更加开朗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.26,0:05:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我给人那样的感觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.45,0:05:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有心烦的事情可以和我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.11,0:05:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么东西我天川都会接受的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.39,0:05:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天川  那话听上去有点H
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文绪 我可不是那个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.11,0:05:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受？ 用哪里？接受什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.25,0:05:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.67,0:05:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说那个接受啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海 我真的不是那个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这副表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.94,0:05:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那样的笑脸去见她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纵使有什么不开心的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要一笑就能变的开朗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.53,0:05:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她面前请保持那样的笑脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之老是逗人家玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 不骗你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出院后一起去吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.57,0:06:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的装了这样满满一大碗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好期待哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经这么晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.86,0:06:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要学习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.67,0:06:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会再来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还想和孝之多呆一会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.34,0:06:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.80,0:06:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之不想和我在一起？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想一直和遥在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.33,0:06:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里和遥说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.76,0:06:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能忘掉很多烦心事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心情也得到放松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.18,0:06:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之能在我身边是最幸福的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.17,0:06:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.47,0:06:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？  遥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.92,0:06:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点好起来  遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点出院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和从前一样大家一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.96,0:07:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从前？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起 她的时间就停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在受到打击的话\N我也不知道会有何后果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.68,0:07:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以绝不能告诉她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.04,0:07:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...最近太忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是应付不过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.92,0:07:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像时间过了很久一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.02,0:07:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.89,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.63,0:07:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想可以一直就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.45,0:08:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.06,0:08:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘记买香波了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎么办好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去蛮可怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.64,0:08:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白天那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.64,0:08:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公交车上碰到的\N是你公司的同事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.90,0:08:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是石田小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.40,0:08:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很会照顾人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 看来你工作很忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月也喝一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.07,0:08:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.78,0:09:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.99,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么变化吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平常一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平常一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.46,0:09:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.76,0:09:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.42,0:09:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过遥看上去那么精神真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快努力好起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总呆在医院里很无聊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.87,0:10:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  孝之常来看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.23,0:10:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.78,0:10:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然学习很忙 但还是每天都来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.37,0:10:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.58,0:10:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都陪在我身边  一直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之很温柔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.77,0:10:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总是告诉我很多有趣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.01,0:10:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里明白了一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.75,0:10:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好喜欢孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.54,0:10:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.92,0:10:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？突然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.69,0:10:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.48,0:10:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会离开我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会一直和我在一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.14,0:11:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.86,0:11:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕孝之可能一去不返
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.75,0:11:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我去看遥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.81,0:11:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着她的眼\N就觉得像要被吸进去一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再去看遥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想见她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.81,0:11:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我和遥的父母约好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.43,0:11:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在遥康复前会协助治疗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这些？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.06,0:11:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你这么关心遥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和她不是已经结束了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.25,0:11:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者是还没有结束？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.75,0:11:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么结束 无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥也是你的朋友吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.85,0:12:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不再是朋友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.59,0:12:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我背叛了遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还对遥的事故感到自责吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.46,0:12:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在同情遥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还喜欢她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不去见她就满意了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.37,0:13:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是捡了狗食吃了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平时的话早就嬉皮笑脸地回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.04,0:13:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼  肯定是被甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.43,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空发情还不如给我好好工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你能留下加班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.79,0:13:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 反正我也有空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.39,0:13:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后换班我也会听您安排的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.55,0:13:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就帮大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.22,0:13:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意她俩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 很在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.66,0:13:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因为她们的待客态度\N或是工作上的原因吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是出于个人的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.78,0:13:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.14,0:13:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 但这是不是有点不太妥当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.90,0:13:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这里毕竟是工作的地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且年龄差距也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.24,0:13:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  正好就是那个年龄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.55,0:14:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.11,0:14:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有个女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.48,0:14:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来现在也应该到那个年龄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.16,0:14:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当初能多和她在一起就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对她来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.72,0:14:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从病房窗户看到的风景\N便是整个世界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.74,0:14:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之  今天没有来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（冰箱里有早饭，用微波炉热一下吃吧）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（我走了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.25,0:15:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总共2625元  收您3000元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.44,0:15:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 要出去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.47,0:15:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪？我以为你今天休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买了很多东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长说希望我多多去帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.94,0:15:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正也不去医院了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.41,0:15:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间可以自由利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三号桌的好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.86,0:16:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.32,0:16:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忙得头昏眼花了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是晚饭时间啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.49,0:16:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穷人们到吃饭的时候就会聚集起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.77,0:16:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真由  六号桌要点菜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.59,0:16:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.51,0:16:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道… 遥出什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.13,0:17:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屎壳郎  还不快回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.32,0:17:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是去丢个垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.49,0:17:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要磨蹭到什么时候  蠢货
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  这里是SKY TEMPLE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.79,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  请稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.00,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之前辈  你的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.80,0:17:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.87,0:17:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是鸣海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.50,0:17:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.46,0:17:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我觉得我们应该好好谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能去你那儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.55,0:17:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些话以后再说也可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.59,0:17:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屎壳郎到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这忙得要死的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之前辈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.04,0:17:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才接了一个女人的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就慌慌张张的跑出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是鸣海吧 ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.18,0:18:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.87,0:18:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥  你没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.51,0:18:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.35,0:18:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么前几天没来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是约好每天都来的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.59,0:18:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.14,0:18:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备高考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.84,0:18:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别太勉强弄坏了身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之总是很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算辛苦也会硬撑下去的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.43,0:18:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我做不了什么  不过有我在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.45,0:19:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直为孝之祈祷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前两天好寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.27,0:19:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.72,0:19:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.81,0:19:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还担心你是不是讨厌我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对遥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.37,0:20:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.92,0:20:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.39,0:20:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.72,0:20:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想和孝之再去看夏祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次就我们两个单独去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.29,0:20:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等遥康复出院了就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直等着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.73,0:20:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.80,0:20:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想早点和孝之一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.09,0:20:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.87,0:21:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.82,0:21:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用着急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.88,0:21:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有的是时间\N可以慢慢地过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.50,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.30,0:21:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.05,0:22:09.85,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,那熟悉的歸家路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.05,0:22:09.85,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\K80}いつも{\K70}歩{\K40}く{\K85}帰{\K50}り{\K50}{\K60}道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.13,0:22:14.99,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,牽著的手不分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.13,0:22:14.99,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\K80}繋い{\K120}だ手を{\K80}放{\K40}せ{\K70}{\K20}な{\K10}{\K20}い
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.35,0:22:20.24,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然希望此刻永遠停留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.35,0:22:20.24,dmhy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\K80}このま{\K50}{\K200}まいたいけ{\K58}{\K20}れ{\K10}{\K20}ど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.46,0:22:25.20,dmhy2,,0000,0000,0000,,時光流逝依舊
